<p data-index="1007">The company determines the actual interest cost, which represents the maximum amount of interest that it may capitalize during 2020, as shown in <a class="blue" id="c10-fig-0006-1" href="#c10-fig-0006" data-index="1008" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="c10-fig-0006" data-target-data-index="1010"><b data-index="1009">Illustration 10.6</b></a>.</p>
