</div>
<figcaption data-index="1048"><p data-index="1049"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="1050"><b data-index="1051"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c10-fig-0006-1" data-index="1052" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="c10-fig-0006-1" data-target-data-index="1008"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="1053">ILLUSTRATION 10.6</span></a></b> <b data-index="1054">Computation of Actual ­Interest Cost</b></span></p></figcaption>
</figure>
<p data-index="1055">The interest cost that Shalla capitalizes is the lesser of $120,228 (avoidable interest) and $239,500 (actual interest), or $120,228.</p>
<p data-index="1056">Shalla records the following journal entries during 2020.</p>
