</div>
<figcaption data-index="1204"><p data-index="1205"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="1206"><b data-index="1207"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c10-fig-0007-1" data-index="1208" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="c10-fig-0007-1" data-target-data-index="1148"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="1209">ILLUSTRATION 10.7</span></a></b> <b data-index="1210">Capitalized Interest Reported in the Income Statement</b></span></p></figcaption>
