<p data-index="3965"><b data-index="3966"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="3967">E10.7</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="3968">(LO <a href="#h3_00010" data-index="3969" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="h3_00010" data-target-data-index="396">2</a>)</span> <b data-index="3970">(Capitalization of Interest)</b> Harrisburg Furniture Company started construction of a combination office and warehouse building for its own use at an estimated cost of $5,000,000 on ­January&nbsp;1, 2020. Harrisburg expected to complete the building by December 31, 2020. Harrisburg has the following debt obligations outstanding during the construction period.</p>
