<h4 data-index="4167"><span class="red" data-index="4168">Instructions</span></h4>
<p data-index="4169">Prepare journal entries on the books of Duffner Company to record these transactions.</p>
<p data-index="4170"><b data-index="4171"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="4172">E10.13</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="4173">(LO <a href="#h3_0003" data-index="4174" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="h3_0003" data-target-data-index="216">1</a>, <a href="#h3_00022" data-index="4175" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="h3_00022" data-target-data-index="1296">3</a>)</span> <b data-index="4176">(Entries for Acquisition of Assets</b><b data-index="4177">)</b> Presented below is information related to Zonker Company.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="4178"><span class="label" data-index="4179"><b data-index="4180">1.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> On July 6, Zonker Company acquired the plant assets of Doonesbury Company, which had discontinued operations. The appraised value of the property is:</p>
