<p data-index="4703"><b data-index="4704"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="4705">E10.23</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="4706">(LO <a href="#h3_00032" data-index="4707" data-section-index="20" data-section-idref="h3_00032" data-target-data-index="2304">4</a>)</span> <b data-index="4708">(Analysis of Subsequent Expenditures)</b> Plant assets often require expenditures subsequent to acquisition. It is important that they be accounted for properly. Any errors will affect both the balance sheets and income statements for a number of years.</p>
