<p class="latin1" data-index="4861"><span class="label" data-index="4862"><b data-index="4863">5.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> A group of new machines was purchased under a royalty agreement that provides for payment of royalties based on units of production for the machines. The invoice price of the machines was $87,000, freight costs were $3,300, installation costs were $2,400, and royalty payments for 2020 were $17,500.</p>
